<h1>The Creator of Nintendo</h1>
<h2>Fusajiro Yamauchi</h2>
<p>Fusajiro Yamauchi was a Japanese entrepreneur who founded the company that is now known as Nintendo. Yamauchi lived in Kyoto, Japan and had a wife and a daughter.</p>
